summary: An ordinance relating to the use of the south one-half of Block 10, James Division of Green Lake Addition, located on the north side of East 65th Street; between 12th Avenue Northeast and Brooklyn Avenue; rezoning said property for business uses and amending Ordinance No. 45382 as amended, by addding thereto two new sections to be known as Section 2-4 and Section 17-4 respectively.
